msgctxt "callout_box.bc666e02-95bb-4aa8-88d2-8e93f0da8a35.body"
msgid ""
"This season, we explore how to build responsible artificial intelligence. We talk to people who are building trustworthy alternatives and confronting today’s risks to help shape better AI for "
"tomorrow."
msgstr ""
"Dit seizoen ûndersykje wy hoe’t ferantwurde keunstmjittige yntelliginsje boud wurde kin. Wy prate mei minsken dy’t betroubere alternativen bouwe en harren mei de hjoeddeistige risiko’s konfrontearje"
" om bettere AI foar de takomst te foarmjen."

